  [1mCrash Location:[22m

  - Function: [38;2;177;185;249madd_score(Student *s, float score)[39m

  [1mRoot Cause:[22m
  The [38;2;177;185;249mscores[39m pointer in the Student structure is [38;2;177;185;249mNULL[39m (0x0000000000000000).
   When the code tries to dereference this NULL pointer to store a score
  value, it causes a segmentation fault.

  3. Crash occurs due to writing to address 0x0

  [1mIssue:[22m
  The Student structure was created but the [38;2;177;185;249mscores[39m array was never
  allocated memory. The program tries to add scores without first
  allocating memory for the [38;2;177;185;249mscores[39m pointer, leading to a NULL pointer
  dereference.
